                    <h3>Understanding Sleep as Medicine</h3>
                    <p>Quality sleep is when your body repairs tissues, consolidates memories, and processes emotions. During deep sleep, your brain's glymphatic system clears toxins, while your immune system strengthens. This isn't just rest—it's active healing.</p>
                    
