                    <p><strong>Consistent Schedule:</strong> Go to bed and wake up at the same time daily, even on weekends, to strengthen your circadian rhythm.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Advanced Sleep Optimization</h3>
                    <p><strong>Sleep Environment:</strong> Create a sanctuary with blackout curtains, comfortable bedding, and minimal electronic devices. Consider air purification and calming scents like lavender.</p>
